game:decorbazaar-quickstart-text: Thank you for using my mod! This mod adds decorative items to the game. If anyone would love to help develop the mod, please contact me on discord @anyanana. Thank you to @EightTonnesOfCrab on discord for getting the stoves to function as well as the bath! Enjoy! List of Items: Stoves: These stoves currently function as ovens, though not visually. You can still see what is cooking by looking at the UI. Stone Stove Cast Iron Stove Cast Iron Stove with Firewood Cast Iron Stove V2 Cast Iron Fireplace Claw Foot Tub allows for 100 buckets of water to fill up. Washing Tub Linen Basket Clothes Line Red Gingham Carpet Side Tables Wardrobe (Bald Cypress) has slots for clothes. Brass Mirror Brass Table Brass Lamps are functional! Brass Sconce is functional! Brass Bed is functional! Left Cabinet (Bald Cypress) has storage slots. Right Cabinet (Bald Cypress) has storage slots. Top Left Cabinet (Bald Cypress) has storage slots. Top Right Cabinet (Bald Cypress) has storage slots. Open Cabinet Sinks Stone Cabinet & Island has storage slots. Stone Drawer & Island has storage slots. Stone Cabinet Top has storage slots. Stone Shelf has storage slots. Cottage Core Table (Bald Cypress) Cottage Core Stool (Bald Cypress) Bald Cypress Stool Kitchen Clutter Ceramic Yellow Pot Jug Dish Rack Pots and Pans Bread Basket Wall Veggie Storage Tea Sets Spice Rack Kitchen Shelf Bread Box has storage slots and can preserve food. Garden Signs Bee Sign Potting Bench has storage slots for seeds. Seed Storage has storage slots for seeds. Bathroom Clutter Butter Churn Witchy Items Paintings only accessable in creative: Fields of Grain House on the Hill Lone Grave
